d":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"每個公民都係抵抗警黑勾結既義士 <br />\n抗爭者不是暴徒 !"},{"pid":"130f582519485e286c34e8cfa4e4f8eed7f2ab26","tid":1388700,"uid":269578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049029c5bf8ab423a22bb3f27ec9288979d44421","tid":1388700,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選應要排最頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私咁，過埋2047都死左啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"e50c78def380c2e19930d582b642b8408c8461ce","tid":1388700,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"476866027b91355c6aa953ff4cd2d8f72530bfe7","tid":1388700,"uid":81312,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:47:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得一小時人其實已經好好<br />\n「分鐘人」e個terms其實又誇張左既，不過個概念就係好快就集結到一批人抗爭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:11:38.000Z","msg":"concept啫<br />\n我都唔信美國真係一分鐘呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75222e01edfe9ce012c0e881b0816efd818f0b97","tid":1388700,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e50c78def380c2e19930d582b642b8408c8461ce","tid":1388700,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"476866027b91355c6aa953ff4cd2d8f72530bfe7","tid":1388700,"uid":81312,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:47:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得一小時人其實已經好好<br />\n「分鐘人」e個terms其實又誇張左既，不過個概念就係好快就集結到一批人抗爭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:11:38.000Z","msg":"concept啫<br />\n我都唔信美國真係一分鐘呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:14:14.000Z","msg":"消防員咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbcded104a8291fa8454afbe7429e8b938e2632f","tid":1388700,"uid":161185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:17:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68d08bb84efa3d4f0b622d247917b3860ca1a9f6","tid":1388700,"uid":230511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:31:14.000Z","msg":"可以結合現代科技寫個app<br />\n用一個base on香港地圖既簡單遊戲<br />\n遊戲設置一個求救系統，一用求救系統全部用app既人都會即時收到<br />\n但係有幾大問題要解決到：<br />\n定位紀錄被追蹤<br />\n比對家濫用狼來了<br />\nFace check問題"},{"pid":"c1862d9a5745137e64b1691e66a565229e840327","tid":1388700,"uid":128850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:33:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e397f8732c949ef76229211a7add877edd364ffe","tid":1388700,"uid":81312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:46:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcf784c9261ef7ea876996dfbd6cc831e6936262","tid":1388700,"uid":81312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:10:01.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"517e03ff0fe4768f665d3fa92d5bad2a7693551c","tid":1388700,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:11:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55837bdaf5fa6eca9c49c64ce65c25b7d0f265b8","tid":1388700,"uid":81312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:39:20.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"4a4f49cd585f25d708027486921386619c6b664a","tid":1388700,"uid":81312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:40:20.000Z","msg":"推上去"},{"pid":"5d756490235be02c8be3a79e022ae25efe1a5964","tid":1388700,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:40:53.000Z","msg":"罷工好啊"},{"pid":"fc286f867d33dc844699f1c8b5dc32f269392d44","tid":1388700,"uid":81312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:41:40.000Z","msg":"罷工呀！"},{"pid":"a9ab71c212873e0ce0a31abe62565b87e681d1bd","tid":1388700,"uid":81312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:43:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"63bd46d8763ce1d2ca7167f16d68373c3f480e08","tid":1388700,"uid":81312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:49:02.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"3ae5317edce2837d7f01239a1e4b8573abda527b","tid":1388700,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d407b6d491e540b253c371210c37ae77fa0fc33","tid":1388700,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:52:21.000Z","msg":"街坊人！！！"},{"pid":"653fc3c964b843f24125ff3b0e9796ca80457c47","tid":1388700,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76384d965180e6e9bb49d7b3f392b04069d2a6b6","tid":1388700,"uid":67553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:34:07.000Z","msg":"致曾經支持逆權運動的人<br />\n<br />\n6.9 6.12 6.16出過黎<br />\n但如今已經冇再出黎<br />\n甚至唔支持而家逆權運動嘅人<br />\n我好想問你地：當初係因咩事走出黎？<br />\n係反送中？警察濫權？支持學生冇暴動？<br />\n<br />\n咁點解而家唔出黎？<br />\n因為抗爭者掟磚？放火？揸鐵通？阻你返工？搞亂香港？<br />\n<br />\n我想再問：你地而家冇再參與，咁當初參與社運嘅訴求，政府有回應未？解決左未？<br />\n我答你：未，問題只有越揭越多。<br />\n<br />\n- 送中條例唔肯撤回<br />\n<br />\n- 警察濫權惡化至當權：<br />\n1. 沙田新城市圍捕連遊客街坊細路哥都唔放過<br />\n2. 元朗恐襲警黑鄉合作無差別打到市民頭破血流，廝殺列車搬到現實上演<br />\n3. 元朗遊行濫發催淚彈波及民居老人院<br />\n4. 西環衝突放催淚彈如放煙花，仲要過期<br />\n5. 迫頂頭上司張建宗認低威<br />\n<br />\n要數數到2046都未數完，所謂海綿彈，300幾焦耳威力如真槍可射穿金屬板，水炮車出動，用槍瞄酒店住客，刻意推跌遊客，警棍改裝，原告變被告兇鳩細路...我唔仔細數了<br />\n<br />\n就以上呢個幾月所發生嘅事，你又憑乜野去暫停，甚至反對抗爭者嘅支持？我想問，啲磚係掟向市民還是全副武裝嘅警察？抗爭者嘅裝備係咪比警察精良？<br />\n唔係。只係地盤頭盔，絕大部分外科口罩，保鮮紙，普通黑衫黑褲波鞋。<br />\n<br />\n可能你會輕輕咁講：咁就唔好出去啦！<br />\n你講就好容易，但以卵擊石，係需要無比勇氣。<br />\n為嘅除左自己，仲有你地。<br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解行動要不斷升級？係因為政府當我地冇到。口口聲聲話要和平理性表達意見，唔好做違法行為。和理非每一次都有做，但政府有冇聽過？冇。林鄭連出席活動都唔敢對外公佈，面對群眾。當行動升級，換黎係更大打壓，甚至港澳辦話支持警察。<br />\n<br />\n極權政府從來唔需要市民支持，因為冇民意基礎，民意猶如垃圾。而暫停支持同反對逆權運動嘅你，就自己成為政府嘅一隻棋，港澳辦話你地：默默支持政府。<br />\n<br />\n你怪人阻你返工，但有冇諗過元朗恐襲嗰段無警時份，所謂只係39分鐘困獸鬥係有幾難捱。你怪示威者暴力，但又對警察當權視若無睹。<br />\n<br />\n香港好需要你地再次支持，因為運動一但失敗，一定變成第二個新疆。<br />\n既然後無退路，惟有撒手一搏。<br />\n希望你地盡早歸隊，8.5全港大罷工。亦希望有一日，大家可以除下口罩相見，一同呼吸自由嘅空氣。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n8.5 全港大罷工"},{"pid":"6103769bacfbd46935b4faf737948392c30bef98","tid":1388700,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:36:15.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以有個tg channel 做總call 台，有志之士一見字就出動？<br />\n<br />\n為免浪費人手，要喺附近三分鐘路程嘅人先過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37dbec040eb443baeadf8882fe3b19ee8213ec76","tid":1388700,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec9e8f81f23001d1af34d43629706a8fe1d47d0","tid":1388700,"uid":34295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:37:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d8cf74cc584ca87a4ab0388e6c5ffb2c3826d6e","tid":1388700,"uid":124133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0775b166365c847428770b08e41dfe812fcd19","tid":1388700,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f45f6bd0201fdfeafa3ece809b49ed77bab46fac","tid":1388700,"uid":195877,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:19:03.000Z","msg":"39分鐘人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:43:25.000Z","msg":"六點報咗警啦。。"},{"pid":"9ff18cc3116a74a62d16d820b23be5c11828b769","tid":1388700,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:43:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1389186/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1389186/page/1</a>"}]}